					expectation of&nbsp;Xn+1&nbsp;knowing&nbsp;X0,&nbsp;.&nbsp;.&nbsp;.&nbsp;,&nbsp;Xn&nbsp;is&nbsp;equal to&nbsp;Xn.&nbsp;Intuitively, we&nbsp;may&nbsp;think &nbsp;
					of the evolution&nbsp;of&nbsp;the fortune&nbsp;of&nbsp;a player in&nbsp;a fair&nbsp;game: the mean value of&nbsp;the &nbsp;
